Uses of Package
com.hotels.beans.generator.core.mapping

  • Packages that use com.hotels.beans.generator.core.mapping 
    Package Description
    com.hotels.beans.generator.core.mapping
    Provides the models of code blocks that map a source type to a destination type, specialized for different kind of classes, like: mutable, immutable and mixed.
  • Classes in com.hotels.beans.generator.core.mapping used by com.hotels.beans.generator.core.mapping 
    Class Description
    MappingCode
    This is the base class for modeling the code block that maps a source object to a destination object.
    MappingCodeFactory
    A factory to obtain an instance of MappingCode.
